thread.title: JH

author: JH
title: JH
text: I sent in my company's logo and received an email back that, while they could use it, it wasn't high resolution and may not come out looking like I wanted. I received reminder emails while I was working on getting a high res logo. As soon as I sent it in I got a proof back and had my new name tag in hand a few days later. It looks great and I love the magnet backing - it is strong enough that it held through my puffer jacket at an outside event this past weekend!
